nodes.text: The XoLynn 9771 deflector shield generator was a deflector shield generator that was mounted behind the cockpit of the clone Z-95 Headhunter, a multi-purpose starfighter. Between 32 and 34 ABY, Rose Tico, a young female human, told her sister Paige about the generator while they were doing a simulation flight run on a clone Z-95 Headhunter.
The XoLynn 9771 deflector shield generator was first mentioned in the 2016 book Poe Dameron: Flight Log, written by Michael Kogge.
